summary: Speed up grinding away the missions to achieve guildmaster ridiculously fast
descriptionHtml: Simply put this mod adds trapdoors that lead to the varrious holds from within the cistern. they are located close by to the training room. in the training room and near by each trapdoor is daderic battle axes that you can steal. it only takes one axe to complete any beadlem job, and you dont have to worry about the npc's stealing them first. if youre haveing difficulties finding the axes, then i offer you this: look near marketplaces.
author: Undead_Red with help from BelakDeSado
